cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.CL 

The paper focuses on intelligent notification mechanisms that rely on understanding and modeling users' behavior and preferences. This involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SI), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
